## Delete a user

```shell
$ curl 'https://ci.example.com/go/api/users/jdoe' \
      -u 'username:password' \
      -H 'Accept: <%= data.apis.versions.users %>' \
      -X DELETE
```

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: <%= data.apis.versions.users %>; charset=utf-8
```

```json
{
  "message": "User 'jdoe' was deleted successfully."
}
```

Deletes a user.

<aside class="notice">
  You must first <a href='#update-a-user'>disable a user</a> before deleting it.
</aside>


